  <source>Amgen</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to provide data on the safety and efficacy of pegfilgrastim when
      administered on the same day versus the next day of chemotherapy, as measured by the duration
      of grade 4 neutropenia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
